t's incorrect, you'll have to adjust the time zone setting (in the Control Panel's Date/Time item) to agree with your location.
\par }\pard \fi-2160\li2160\widctlpar\tx2160 {\b\f7\fs20 Local time}{\f7\fs20 \tab The current local time and date supplied by your computer's clock.
