\par }{\b\f7\fs20 Moon's distance}{\f7\fs20 \tab Distance of the centre of the Moon from the centre of the Earth, given both in kilometres and Earth radii (approximately 6378.14 kilometres, neglecting equatorial flattening of the globe).
