\par }{\f7\fs20 The algorithms used in Moontool may be found in the following books.  If you're interested in developing software for astronomy, these books are highly recommended.  In addition, }{\i\f7\fs20 Sky & Telescope}{\f7\fs20  magazine has a monthly }{
\i\f7\fs20 Astronomical Computing}{\f7\fs20  column which publishes algorithms and discusses their applications. 
